Yeast extract/ peptone/dextrose (YPD, 1% yeast extract, 2% peptone, 2% dextrose, 2% agar) and synthetic complete (SC, 0.67% yeast nitrogen base without amino acid, 0.087% amino acid mixture, 2% dextrose, 2% agar) media or the corresponding drop-out media were as described in [28, 29] . Homozygous haploid deletion strains library (Parental strain BY4741: MATa his3Δ1 leu2Δ0 met15Δ0 ura3Δ0) was obtained from Thermo Scientific (Pittsburgh, PA, USA). 


